    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbItems} />
      <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">What you need to prepare before your employer files the application</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">
        Every guide about MOHRE work permits is written for employers and PROs. This one is for you — the employee. Your employer handles the Tasheel submission, but you provide the documents. If your degree is wrong, your experience letter is untranslated, or your attestation is incomplete, the application stalls and your start date slips.
      </p>
      <div class="service-snapshot">
        <div class="snapshot-item">
          <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
